g.text: It may sound unrealistic. But when setting up goal, we are inspired by the quote
The reasonable man adapts himself to the world; the unreasonable one persists in
trying to adapt the world to himself. Therefore all progress depends on the
unreasonable man. The worst sin towards our fellow creatures is not to hate them, but
to be indifferent to them: that's the essence of inhumanity.
Own 5%-10% stake in 8-10 profitable unicorn by 2033
Be the pioneer of of carbon capture program & trading
Lead a reforestation move in Cambodia. Aim to have at least 30% of Cambodia reforest
